title: United Kingdom 20 Year Bond Yield
description: UK 20 Year Bond Yield was 3.99 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 20 Year Bond Yield reached an all time high of 5.20 in October of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 20Y.
author: Department of Treasury, UK
